Class By

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.dom.By

  • public class By
extends java.lang.Object
    Allows constructing different find methods for SearchContext.findElement(By) method.
    允许为SearchContext.findElement（By）方法构造不同的查找方法。
